# Defense-in-depth: secrets files normally live OUTSIDE the repo
# (~/.config/cs/secrets.env). These patterns catch the case where
# a user accidentally copies one into the working tree. The `make
# audit-secrets` gate is the second line of defense.
secrets.env
secrets.toml
*.secrets
.envrc
.env
.env.local
